---
import Badge from './Badge.astro';
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
import aboutImg from '../assets/local.jpeg';
---

<section id="local" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="animate-slide-in-left">
        <Badge variant="outline" class="mb-4 border-red-300 text-red-700">
          Nuestro Local
        </Badge>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-red-900 mb-6">Un espacio diseñado para ti</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-red-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          En The Barber Domi hemos creado un ambiente único donde la tradición barbera se combina con el confort
          moderno. Cada detalle está pensado para ofrecerte una experiencia excepcional.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 animate-slide-in-left" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-700 rounded-full animate-pulse-slow"></div>
            <span class="text-red-700">Ambiente relajado y profesional</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 animate-slide-in-left" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-700 rounded-full animate-pulse-slow"></div>
            <span class="text-red-700">Productos premium de alta calidad</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 animate-slide-in-left" style="animation-delay: 0.6s;">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-700 rounded-full animate-pulse-slow"></div>
            <span class="text-red-700">Técnicas tradicionales y modernas</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative animate-slide-in-right">
        <div class="aspect-square bg-red-100 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:scale-105 transform transition-all duration-500">
          <img
            src={aboutImg.src}
            alt="Interior de The Barber Domi"
            width="500"
            height="500"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-1 xl:-right-4 bg-red-700 p-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg animate-float">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
            <Icon name="star" class="h-5 w-5 text-yellow-400" />
            <span class="font-bold text-gray-100">4.9</span>
            <a href="https://booksy.com/es-es/66211_the-barber-domi_barberia_49363_sabadell#ba_s=seo" target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-white text-sm">Booksy Reviews</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
